I"<p>I grew up in <a href="https://warsawtour.pl/en/sightseeing-routes/">Warsaw</a>, Poland’s capital city, and I am ‘the 90’s kid’. I graduated in Environmental Biology from the University of Warsaw. I also studied Computational Methods of Physics at the same university. I defended my Ph.D. at the School of Environmental Sciences, University of East Anglia in Norwich, UK.</p>

<p>Since then, I have worked as a bio-modeller and a bioinformatician in research institutes in Warsaw, Poznań and now in Paris.</p>

<p>For more detailed info on projects I did, see the tab <a href="/3_RESEARCH"><strong>RESEARCH</strong></a>.</p>

